If artesunate is not available, use artemether in preference to quinine for treating children and adults with severe malaria.<br>
&nbsp;
<p class="statement" style="background-color:rgb( 255 , 153 , 0 );  padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 5px;"><span style="color:#ffffff"><em>Conditional recommendation, low-certainty evidence</em></span></p></tbody>
